title: Integra Type R Expo 12
description: In car footage of the Eibach "demo" car from last week's ITR Expo 12 at Mid Ohio Sports Car Course.  This was a very lightly modded '98 ITR with Toyo RA1 tires and Eibach Multi Pro R2 coilovers driven by Eibach employee Tony Jackson and owned by Steve LaClair.  The only other performance mods were a Mugen intake and SMSP header.
tags: Eibach, performance suspension, Acura Integra Type R, Eibach Multi Pro R2 Coilovers
